Cell["\<\
- The API returns at most 1001 features per request.
- Large queries without spatial bounds may be slow or hit server-side compute \
limits.
- The GEEComputeFeatures::apierr message surfaces the actual GEE API error \
when a request fails (e.g., invalid asset name).
- Passing an IMAGE or IMAGE_COLLECTION asset instead of a TABLE asset will fai\
